SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This session can be used to get date ranges for certain period types. It uses the VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS view, and you pass in the CLM_LOCK_CD and APC_STAT_CD values. It puts out the MIN/MAX Quarter period and Monthly periods, along with their associated Start and End dates, based on what values you pass in. Since it builds a Parameter file for use in another session, you also need to pass in the Folder, Workflow, and the Worklet or Session that will be using the new Parameter file.

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT VAPC_DETAIL.PERIOD_ID, VAPC_DETAIL.RBATE_ID, VAPC_DETAIL.RAC, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_SRC_CODE, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_LVL_ID1, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_LVL_ID2, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_LVL_ID3, VAPC_DETAIL.NDC, SUM(VAPC_DETAIL.INGRD_CST) INGRD_CST, SUM(VAPC_DETAIL.RBATE_ACCESS), SUM(VAPC_DETAIL.RBATE_MRKT_SHR), SUM(VAPC_DETAIL.RBATE_ADMIN_FEE), VAPC_DETAIL.INV_MODEL, SUM(VAPC_DETAIL.CNTRC_FEE_PAID) CNTRC_FEE_PAID, SUM(VAPC_DETAIL.AMT_TAX ) AMT_TAX, VAPC_DETAIL.XR007_CG_NB, YEAR(VAPC_DETAIL.DSPND_DATE) DSPND_YY, MONTH(VAPC_DETAIL.DSPND_DATE) DSPND_MM FROM RPS.VAPC_DETAIL VAPC_DETAIL WHERE VAPC_DETAIL.PERIOD_ID = $$MAX_RPSDM_PERIOD_ID GROUP BY VAPC_DETAIL.PERIOD_ID, VAPC_DETAIL.RBATE_ID, VAPC_DETAIL.RAC, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_SRC_CODE, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_LVL_ID1, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_LVL_ID2, VAPC_DETAIL.EXTNL_LVL_ID3, VAPC_DETAIL.XR007_CG_NB, VAPC_DETAIL.NDC, VAPC_DETAIL.INV_MODEL, YEAR(VAPC_DETAIL.DSPND_DATE), MONTH(VAPC_DETAIL.DSPND_DATE)

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, var_dspnd_prd < var_qtr_str_prd, var_qtr_str_prd, var_dspnd_prd > var_qtr_end_prd, var_qtr_end_prd, var_dspnd_prd)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: DSPND_PRD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX.MEDD_DRUG_CD as MEDD_DRUG_CD, KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX.NDC_NB as NDC_NB, SUBSTR(CHAR(KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX.EFF_DT),1,4) || SUBSTR(CHAR(KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX.EFF_DT),6,2) as EFF_DT, SUBSTR(CHAR(KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX.END_DT),1,4)|| SUBSTR(CHAR(KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX.END_DT),6,2) as END_DT FROM $$MVS_DB2_OWNER.KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX KSRB520_RDS_NDC_EX

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: NDC_NB = NDC_in AND EFF_DT <= DSPND_PRD_in AND END_DT >= DSPND_PRD_in

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_NB as PRCS_NB, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_TYP_CD as PRCS_TYP_CD, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_FILE_NM as PRCS_FILE_NM, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_FILE_CRTE_DT as PRCS_FILE_CRTE_DT, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.REC_CNT_VL as REC_CNT_VL, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRD_TYP_CD as PRD_TYP_CD, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRD_DT as PRD_DT, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_BEG_TS as PRCS_BEG_TS, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_END_TS as PRCS_END_TS, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_CO_ID as PRCS_CO_ID, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_PMT_SCHD_CD as PRCS_PMT_SCHD_CD, KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_STAT_CD as PRCS_STAT_CD FROM $$MVS_DB2_OWNER.KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK WHERE KSZ6005_PCNTL_TRK.PRCS_TYP_CD = 15

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: PERIOD_ID = PERIOD_ID1 AND DSPND_PRD = DSPND_PRD1 AND RBATE_ID = RBATE_ID1 AND RAC = RAC1 AND EXTNL_SRC_CODE = EXTNL_SRC_CODE1 AND EXTNL_LVL_ID1 = EXTNL_LVL_ID11 AND EXTNL_LVL_ID2 = EXTNL_LVL_ID21 AND EXTNL_LVL_ID3 = EXTNL_LVL_ID31 AND XR007_CG_NB = XR007_CG_NB1 AND INV_MODEL = INV_MODEL1
